<L>__{exterior building. day}
<A>__{it is a typical, modern, multi purpose office building. we hear the sounds of grunting, bumping and clanging.}
<L>__{interior lobby. day}
<A>__{there is something of a commotion going on at one of the elevators. vera, and a small, well meaning crowd, are trying to get mark and his gurney inside. it will not fit horizontally. as they angle it up, mark begins to panic.}
<C>__{mark}
<D>__{it won't fit. it's not going to fit. let's go back.}
<A>__{a muscular latino guy reassures him.}
<C>__{latino}
<D>__{hey, it's fine. we got you. this is going to work just fine.}
<A>__{vera guides him.}
<C>__{vera}
<D>__{the top has to go over to the left.}
<C>__{mark}
<D>__{i don't feel so good about this. let's forget it.}
<A>__{the latino guy takes no notice. vera is flushed and angry.}
<C>__{vera}
<D>__{look, do you want to see this woman or not?}
<C>__{mark}
<D>__{no!}
<A>__{one more heave and the gurney goes in with a jolt.}
<C>__{mark }
<D>__{aah!}
<C>__{vera}
<D>__{well, it's too late.}
